Class DefaultVisualizationDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ptc.core.components.visualization.AbstractVisualizationDelegate
      • com.ptc.core.components.visualization.DefaultVisualizationDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VisualizationDelegate

    public class DefaultVisualizationDelegate
extends AbstractVisualizationDelegate
    Default delegate shows no visualization. Types that need to show visualization should extend the AbstractVisualizationDelegate and define the showVisualization() API to return the appropriate html for the type.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
